ipax-cli
========

This project depends on @ipax/core (../packages/core) for the IPAX scoring
engine. See ../packages/core/NOTICE for full attribution of the code
derived from third-party sources (IPAX 2 by Santiago Bustelo, and the
APCA W3 algorithm by Andrew Somers / Myndex Research) — none of that code
is duplicated here.


Original work in this repository
---------------------------------
The following files are original contributions not derived from the above:
  index.js          — CLI entry point and argument parsing
  parse-color.js    — universal color parser (hex, rgb, oklch, color-mix, named)
  ipax-find.js      — OKLCh grid search command
  ipax-palette.js   — palette ΔE matrix and CVD simulation
  ipax-stack.js     — layer compositor and stack scoring
